name: Rebirth blossom
description:
Inspired by @luana.angioletti and motivated by @yakudoo, @al_oner_one and @DiscoWarlock.

Curiously, what was the main aim of this work, a challenge, became much more of a self-discovery journey, which is deeply tied with being able to pay for therapy with NFT earnings. This space allowed many of us to see ourselves as creators and to push us towards new experiments, such as HEN itself.

Ambient best enjoyed with 🔊 🎧

Controls
Mouse / Hold the crosshair = look around
WASD / Arrows / Left mushroom = move like a joystick
Space bar / Right mushroom = jump
H / Bottom arrow = hide UI

If your browser is not locking the mouse, click "view on ipfs" on the page footer or IPFS link under Properties. You can also try:
Lock mouse = L
Fullscreen = F
